  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Visit Europe's most striking mountain range and Italy's largest lake on this diverse multi-centre holiday.</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to the <a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites">Dolomites</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> means you get to experience the best of both worlds. Spend a few days walking through some incredible mountain backdrops before swapping the footpaths and mountain huts of <a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/3fa9c9a6e8a74eb1acb0f3c5104f4820" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3fa9c9a6e8a74eb1acb0f3c5104f4820}" title="Madonna di Campiglio" data-anchor="#">Madonna di Campiglio</a> in the Dolomites area for the gently-lapping waters of Lake Garda in either <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89a5238595c34e53a5ef4c989b459fce}" title="Malcesine">Malcesine</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/689f022eb7974a7087ccbecf4adbda43" href="/{localLink:umb://document/689f022eb7974a7087ccbecf4adbda43}" title="Garda">Garda</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a>.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,671pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>7, 10, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel on Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Return airport transfers to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Taxi transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
<li>Up to two included guided walks per person per week if staying in Selva, Merano, Garda, Bardolino or Limone</li>
</ul>
</ul>
