  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in The Dolomites</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e8557eec82d947e89e7aa9047035cce1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8557eec82d947e89e7aa9047035cce1}" title="Hotel Mignon">Hotel Mignon, Selva</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13078924/hotel-mignon-selva-exterior.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="mignon" data-udi="umb://media/00e21e4655154938a7bf145d88498b71" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Mignon offers friendly hospitality and stylish interiors with comfortable guest rooms, a wonderful restaurant and state-of-the-art spa. This is our most popular hotel in Selva, so make sure you book your room before they're all gone!</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella">Hotel Rodella, Selva</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13091219/rodella-12-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="rodella" data-udi="umb://media/53efc0cc88c94665a457d41ac4f85a9c" /></p>
<p>The family-run Rodella is a perfect base for walkers - just 15 minutes from the nearest lift with a free shuttle bus on request. This is an idyllic mountain retreat, in a perfect location for walking and complete with a modern wellness area and fantastic local food.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8d7a83200b954c858bcfb2007c1d6644" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8d7a83200b954c858bcfb2007c1d6644}" title="Park Hotel Mignon">Park Hotel Mignon, Merano</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13079822/park_hotel_mignon_pool.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="park hotel mignon" data-udi="umb://media/5d645e55f5554f8c835eb5fbfd26af9d" /></p>
<p><span>The Park Hotel Mignon is one of Merano’s finest hotels. It's in a fantastic central location and has an outdoor pool and spa area. When it comes to dining, expect fantastic gourmet food made with some of the finest ingredients in the South Tyrol.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in the Dolomites</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Lake Garda</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0ef96c55540749d8bc44592840cbb7b4}" title="Hotel Europa SkyPool &amp; Panorama">Hotel Europa Skypool &amp; Panorama, Riva</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13100137/adobestock_158586247-1-2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Europa" data-udi="umb://media/b9e64f89be7d46a4a70ee879841aa534" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Europa has one of the best locations on Riva's harbour. It overlooks the historic centre and is just a few steps from the ferry port.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/582c1440c43347c6a27756575d766e8e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/582c1440c43347c6a27756575d766e8e}" title="Hotel Garden">Hotel Garden, Garda</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13089991/garden.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Garden, Garda" data-udi="umb://media/6814360e88f04ac5bbb1631ece203016" />Hotel Garden is next to Garda's bustling lakefront promenade yet still manages to feel secluded. It's got large, peaceful gardens where you'll find a pool with lake views. The gardens are the perfect place to relax on your summer holiday. The interiors are traditional and welcoming and the family that run the hotel treat every guest as an old family friend. </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/5da496c82269489c9f9033e4280d7813" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5da496c82269489c9f9033e4280d7813}" title="Hotel Bellevue San Lorenzo">Hotel Bellevue San Lorenzo, Malcesine</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13077492/ita_mal_belsanlor_01mb-2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="bellevue san lorenzo" data-udi="umb://media/9f5cf72c2aa64ba69113fc54a5a3d7bf" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Bellevue San Lorenzo is in the most beautiful setting a short walk along the lakeside from the centre of Malcesine. A lake-view infinity pool takes pride of place in the gardens. This is a very peaceful adults only hotel, with large gardens full of olive trees and roses.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Lake Garda</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
