  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Explore the best of the Dolomites &amp; Lake Garda on this multi-centre holiday. You'll start in the mountains in chilled out Selva, historic Merano or activity centric Madonna di Campiglio before heading down to lively Lake Garda.</p>]]></listingDescription>
