  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you mix and match hotels, lengths of stay, and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from guided walks and outdoor adventures to relaxing lakeside days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<p><strong>Explore the Dolomites on foot (and gondola) and enjoy the local cuisine</strong></p>
<p>The Dolomites will take your breath away. Heading up to the panoramic viewpoints on a clear day and taking in valley views or gazing in awe at the jagged peaks surrounding you is one of the best ways to relax on holiday. Not only is the scenery and walking out of this world, but we love the Austrian/Italian fusion cuisine of the Tyrolean region, featuring, meat, cheese, potatoes and traditional dishes like kaisershmarrn or spetzle. Not to mention the delicious wine on offer. The Dolomites are the perfect place to come for your summer getaway.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f7e065ba2a3d40d7893ad1b116880496}" title="The Dolomites" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About The Dolomites</a></p>
<p><strong>Relax by Lake Garda or discover hidden walking trails</strong></p>
<p>Lake Garda is one of our most popular destinations during the summer and it’s easy to understand why. You’ll find people sitting in restaurants along the shores of the lake enjoying the views, strolling along promenades or hitting one of the walking trails for the best panoramas of Lake Garda. It’s easy to get around the lake with the frequent ferries so make sure you explore the nearby towns.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Lake Garda</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></locationDescription>
